== 开发与制作 ==
2010年6月9日，USA电视台决定预订《共同法则》的试映集，由科马克·威布里和玛瑞安妮·威布里负责撰写试映集剧本。<ref>{{Cite web|url=http://www.deadline.com/2010/06/usa-network-picks-up-common-law/|title=USA Network Picks Up 'Common Law' Pilot|date=June 9, 2010|last=Andreeva|first=Nellie|work=[[Deadline.com|Deadline.com]]|accessdate=August 18, 2011|archive-date=2012-10-12|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20121012144647/http://www.deadline.com/2010/06/usa-network-picks-up-common-law/|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref name="greenlight"/>2010年8月，试镜公告发布，迈克尔·伊雷成为最先敲定的演员。<ref name="ealy">{{Cite web|url=http://www.deadline.com/2010/08/michael-ealy-set-as-lead-in-usa-networks-pilot-common-law/|title=Michael Ealy Set As Lead In USA Network's Pilot 'Common Law'|date=August 16, 2010|last=Andreeva|first=Nellie|work=Deadline.com|accessdate=August 18, 2011|archive-date=2012-10-12|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20121012144714/http://www.deadline.com/2010/08/michael-ealy-set-as-lead-in-usa-networks-pilot-common-law/|dead-url=no}}</ref>之后，沃伦·科尔确定饰演伊雷的搭档。<ref>{{Cite web|url=http://www.deadline.com/2010/12/24-alum-warren-kole-to-star-in-usa-pilot-common-law/|title='24' Alum Warren Kole To Star In USA Pilot 'Common Law'|date=December 8, 2010|last=Ausiello|first=Michael|work=Deadline.com|accessdate=August 18, 2011|archive-date=2012-10-12|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20121012144739/http://www.deadline.com/2010/12/24-alum-warren-kole-to-star-in-usa-pilot-common-law/|dead-url=no}}</ref>

2011年6月，据报道称，USA电视台即将决定将《共同法则》开发为剧集，条件是对于剧集设定进行部分调整，包括增加更多的动作戏份，并更换了饰演艾玛·瑞安医生的演员。<ref name="acker">{{Cite web|url=http://www.deadline.com/2011/06/buddy-cop-pilot-common-law-nears-series-order-at-usa-will-undergo-some-tweaking/|title=Buddy Cop Pilot 'Common Law' Nears Series Order At USA, Will Undergo Some Tweaking|date=June 14, 2011|last=Andreeva|first=Nellie|work=[[Deadline.com|Deadline.com]]|accessdate=August 18, 2011|archive-date=2012-10-12|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20121012144620/http://www.deadline.com/2011/06/buddy-cop-pilot-common-law-nears-series-order-at-usa-will-undergo-some-tweaking/|dead-url=no}}</ref>2011年7月6日，USA电视台同意预订该剧，计划于2012年夏播出11集。<ref name="greenlight"/>在2011年11月29日时，该剧的首播时间被提前到2012年1月26日，<ref name="premiere date" />但是后来又被推后到原定的夏季档，定于2012年5月11日开始首播。<ref name="final premiere date">{{cite web|url=http://tvbythenumbers.zap2it.com/2012/03/02/usa-sets-common-law-premiere-date-for-friday-may-11-at-109c/122774/|title=USA Sets 'Common Law' Premiere Date For Friday, May 11 At 10/9c|publisher=TV by the Numbers|date=March 2, 2012|accessdate=March 2, 2012|first=Amanda|last=Kondolojy|archive-date=2016-03-05|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160305004725/http://tvbythenumbers.zap2it.com/2012/03/02/usa-sets-common-law-premiere-date-for-friday-may-11-at-109c/122774/|dead-url=yes}}</ref>

2011年10月14日，该剧开始在[[路易斯安那州|路易斯安那州]][[新奥尔良|新奥尔良]]拍摄。<ref name="Louisiana Entertainment2">{{cite web|title=Production Hotline|url=http://louisianaentertainment.gov/film/resumes.cfm|publisher=Louisiana Film & Television|accessdate=4 December 2011|archive-date=2011-12-03|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20111203215552/http://www.louisianaentertainment.gov/Film/resumes.cfm|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref name="Louisiana Entertainment1">{{cite news|title=USA Network to Practice 'Common Law' With New Series|url=http://www.thewrap.com/tv/article/usa-network-practice-common-law-new-series-28824|accessdate=4 December 2011|newspaper=The Wrap|date=5 July 2011|archive-date=2017-02-08|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170208134228/http://www.thewrap.com/tv/article/usa-network-practice-common-law-new-series-28824/|dead-url=no}}</ref>

